query: prefix dbpo: <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/> prefix foaf: <http://xmlns.com/foaf/0.1/> select distinct ?title, ?pict, ?label, ?abstract where {<http://dbpedia.org/resource/Isaac_I_Komnenos> dbpo:title ?title ; foaf:depiction ?pict ; rdfs:label ?label ; dbpo:abstract ?abstract FILTER ( lang(?abstract) = "en" )}

prefix dbpo: <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/> prefix foaf: <http://xmlns.com/foaf/0.1/> select distinct ?title, ?pict, ?label, ?abstract where {<http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gordian_III> dbpo:title ?title ; foaf:depiction ?pict ; rdfs:label ?label ; dbpo:abstract ?abstract FILTER ( lang(?abstract) = "en" )}
select distinct ?book ?isbn where{?book dbpprop:name "Junie B. Jones"@en. optional {?book dbpprop:isbn ?isbn.}}
select distinct ?book ?isbn where{?book dbpprop:name "The Lord of the Rings"@en. optional {?book dbpprop:isbn ?isbn.}}
select distinct ?book ?isbn where{?book dbpprop:name "Nontan"@en. optional {?book dbpprop:isbn ?isbn.}}

select ?s ?o where {
   ?s dbpprop:fullname "Robin van Persie"@en
}
